The basic syntax for anchors is:

<<wikitext-example src:"A paragraph with an invisible anchor. ^BlockLevelLinksID1">>

# Add a space between the end of your text and the `^`.
# There is no space between `^` and the id.
# ID can contain any Unicode char other than `^` and space ` `.

The anchor becomes an attribute of the enclosing block element. The DOM will have:

```html
<p data-tw-anchor="BlockLevelLinksID1" id="Block Level Links in WikiText^^BlockLevelLinksID1">...</p>
```

